# Override .gitignore patterns to include these directories in Cursor indexing
# These are excluded from git but useful for AI context when debugging tests
#
# NOTE: The ! negation syntax is documented to override .gitignore but is known
# to be buggy (see: forum.cursor.com/t/bug-prefix-in-gitignore-and-cursorignore-is-not-honored)
# We include these patterns anyway in anticipation of future bug fixes.

# All logs (pytest, llm, orchestra)
!logs/
!logs/**
!logs/*
